high_descs: Head rotate and walk towards near the bed.
Turn left and walk towards the bed.
Pick the spoon from the bed and turn left and walk towards the sink.
Put the ladle inside the sink and wash it.
Pick it back and turn right and turn right and then turn left.
Place the ladle on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: To place the ladle on the CoffeeTable.

high_descs: Walk out of the bedroom and go in the bedroom using the door in the living room to reach the bed.
Pick up a ladle that is on the bed.
Take the spoon and go to the sink.
Put the ladle in the sink, wash it and then remove it from the sink.
Take the spoon and go to the coffeetable.
Put the ladle down on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Getting a clean ladle to put on the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn right and turn left and head around move towards the bed.
Pick the ladle from the bed.
Turn right and turn left and turn left move towards the sink.
Place the ladle inside the sink, pick the ladle from the sink.
Turn left move towards the coffeetable.
Place the ladle on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: To place the ladle on the coffeetable.
